Kriege<br>
45 Tri-Spec Cleric</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#c0c0c0><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub79.ezboard.com/blighttanksofdaoc.showUserPublicProfile?gid=demised>Demised</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Seasoned Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 148<br> <font color=#000000>(10/1/03 6:43 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=358.topic&index=11>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The question...</span><hr size=1> I'm with Nirala...<br>
<br>
As a 50 Thrust Merc, the only NON-DW style I have on my quickbar is Dragonfang... <p>Vith<br>
