<br>
Don't compare your brother's inf DW with your merc's DW. Infs did not get a damage boost with v1.62, just mercs. Our DW line is no longer the same as inf. Delve them and compare, the Herald is still showing old damage rates. My inf has almost nothing in DW. Crit strike line is in a world of it's own.  <p>Callan McSlaughter<br>
4x Crush Mercenary Igraine</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#c0c0c0><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub79.ezboard.com/blighttanksofdaoc.showUserPublicProfile?gid=vasagh>Vasagh</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 85<br> <font color=#000000>(10/2/03 12:26 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=358.topic&index=13>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The question...</span><hr size=1> I only use dual shadows in RvR from the dw line. <br>
<br>
Ametyst and backslash are my most common styles all from slash spec. I have diamond slash on main bar too but I use it occasionally.<br>
<br>
I have reflection/hypnotic chain on 2nd bar for pve or rare 1v1. (I don't solo much nowadays, preferring to run guild groups)<br>
